\SE\SE[0] Welcome to 'Lunaroa CATCH!!' \!\SE[0] This 'shitty
game' is a 'game' where you collect a lot of 'Laura' from
the 'Lunaroa special edition'!

\SE[17]Shitty game...!! \SE[16]Are you asking me to bring
something that was really fun here? Is it Vita's shitty
game...!?

\SE[4]Hey, what does shitty game mean? \SE[3]It might be the
first time I've heard that word.

\SE[16]Don't you know about shitty games either!?
\SE[15]It's actually a game that's too shitty...! \SE[17]In
this day and age, there are even people who make a fortune
from shitty games!
\SE[17] (I feel like I've heard something similar before...)

\SE[54] Vita, hurry up...! I... can't wait anymore...!!
\SE[23] I want that quickly...!
\SE[4] (Wow. I've never seen such a mama before...)

\SE[12]Hehe~! I don't mind being wanted! \SE[13]Well then,
let's get started right away...!

\SE[4]Wow...! So many Lauras are falling...!! \SE[2]What
kind of magic are you using...!?
